activities.name: If run 1st and END of Month

source.sqlReaderQuery:
select 1 
from dbo.dim_Date t1
where CalendarDate = cast (getdate() as date)
and (DayOfMonth in (1,2) or DateMonthEnd =FORMAT (getdate(), 'yyyy-MM-dd'))
UNION 
select 0 
from dbo.dim_Date t1
where CalendarDate = cast (getdate() as date)
and (DayOfMonth not in (1,2) and DateMonthEnd <> FORMAT (getdate(), 'yyyy-MM-dd' ))
